// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2702 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3d308c28-a292-57a1-84ee-866ca26aed15

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
